AddressInfo.Title: Garden Route Mall (George)
AddressInfo.AccessComments: Enter the round-about closest to the McDonald's restaurant and take the first exit. Drive towards the Wimpy and FNB ATM, the charge point is located behind that building, closest to wall of the main centre. The DC fast charger is located in the open parking lot, behind the Wimpy and situated closest to the centre wall.
